  "title": "ISic000823. Statue base for Hieron II of Syracuse",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Unknown</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"Βασιλέος\">Βασιλέος</span>  <span data-text=\"ἁγε\">ἁγε</span>  <span data-text=\"μόνος\">[μόνος]</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"̒Ιέρωνος\">̒Ιέρωνος</span>  <span data-text=\"Ἱεροκλέος\">Ἱεροκλέος</span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"Συρακόσιοι\">Συρακόσιοι</span>  <span data-text=\"θεοῖς\">θεοῖς</span>  <span data-text=\"πᾶσι\">πᾶσι</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Unknown</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"Βασιλέος\">ΒΑΣΙΛΕΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἁγε\">ΑΓΕ</span><span data-text=\"μόνος\">[.....]</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"̒Ιέρωνος\">̒ΙΕΡΩΝΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"Ἱεροκλέος\">ΙΕΡΟΚΛΕΟΣ</span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-text=\"Συρακόσιοι\">ΣΥΡΑΚΟΣΙΟΙ</span><span data-text=\"θεοῖς\">ΘΕΟΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"πᾶσι\">ΠΑΣΙ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic000823_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic000823_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic000823.jpg\"><img title=\"Photo J. Prag, Aut. Assessorato Beni Culturali Regione Siciliana n.10681 del 06/05/2014\" src=\"ISic000823-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of Kaibel (IG)</span></span>; </li><li><span class=\"Line 1\">Line.1: <span>ἁγε[ομένου], Dittenberger</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>The Syracusans (dedicate this statue) of the king and hegemon Hieron, son of Hierokles, to all the gods</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>As John Ma, Statues and Cities (Oxford 2013) 20 n.27 notes, this is an anomalous instance of an honorific dedication where the honorand is in the genitive</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 56.1103.1.1 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> 3231 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817</a></li><li> Franz 1853 5368 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250</a></li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">2</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a></li><li> Dittenberger 1915-1924 no.427 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000727\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000727</a></li><li> Libertini 1929 123 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001872\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001872</a></li><li> De Sensi Sestito 1977 82 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002043\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002043</a></li><li> Dimartino 2006 no.1.1 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002022\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002022</a></li><li> Dimartino 2017 241-246 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10003125\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10003125</a>  </li><li> Prag 2017 122 fig.5 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001664\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001664</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p> Types list: <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Β-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Β type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Β-type2.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Β type2.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Γ-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Γ type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Γ-type2.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Γ type2.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3.1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Ε-type2.3.2.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ε type2.3.2</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Θ-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Θ type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Θ-type1.4.html\" target=\"_blank\">Θ type1.4</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/dat